    "description": "游戏以动画世界为背景，你需要一路射击、格挡、闪避驾驶者笨重载具漫天乱飞的滑稽敌人。偷取敌人的废料，升级你的技能，制作疯狂又实用的武器！你能坚持多久呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/62e32aeb9213363737a33c0b7b3adfdb.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/62e32aeb9213363737a33c0b7b3adfdb.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/62e32aeb9213363737a33c0b7b3adfdb.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《GAZZLERS》专为VR打造，让你全程紧绷每一根神经，通过物理瞄准、格挡、闪避应对一波又一波的子弹！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/8ddefcade4ef44f8ab93fb383775321b.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/8ddefcade4ef44f8ab93fb383775321b.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/8ddefcade4ef44f8ab93fb383775321b.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你寻获的每一项新武器和升级内容都会对你的枪械和游玩风格产生影响。将你找到的部件组装成终极武器吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/3b5b76b3259ab81f24ee8d5d9afa347a.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/3b5b76b3259ab81f24ee8d5d9afa347a.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/3b5b76b3259ab81f24ee8d5d9afa347a.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏结束了？没关系！每一次死亡之后，你都可以继承废料。升级你的技能树，然后以更强大的姿态从头再来！<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>新增挑战：：完成每日和每周挑战，赢取更多废料！<br></li><li>新增难度选项：开启全新梦魇模式，挑战自己的新极限，逐步登顶排行榜！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/7ffd4c169a0b2d4428f687a4dbc11867.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/7ffd4c169a0b2d4428f687a4dbc11867.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/7ffd4c169a0b2d4428f687a4dbc11867.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
